.SH DESCRIPTION
.sp
Functions MPI_Graphdims_get and \fI\%MPI_Graph_get\fP retrieve the
graph\-topology information that was associated with a communicator by
MPI_Graph_create\&.
.sp
The information provided by MPI_Graphdims_get can be used to
dimension the vectors \fBindex\fP and \fBedges\fP correctly for a call to
\fI\%MPI_Graph_get\fP\&.
